commit message:
added ukrainian localization

Signed-off-by: Andriy Kopanytsia <andriykopanytsia@gmail.com>

Fixed misleading translations.

The translations mean 'Copied ... to clipboard'.
I modified them to 'Tap here to copy ... to clipboard'.
Fix APP_ABI support for ndk r8b.
Fix crash in key generation on x86 devices.

profile time spent within each thread

From Mike Mohr
